humanMachineDialogue.author: ZS Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The N stage is determined by the presence and extent of cancer in the lymph nodes. In this report, the right axillary sentinel lymph node biopsy showed no metastatic tumor (0/1), while the left axillary lymph node dissection revealed metastatic carcinoma in two of twenty-four lymph nodes (2/24). Therefore, the N stage is N1.
